videos.description: Iowa QB Nathan Stanley finds WR Nick Easley for a 25-yard gain early in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Iowa offense attacking early

videos.description: Iowa RB Akrum Wadley bounces to the outside for a 12-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Wadley puts Hawkeyes on board with TD

videos.description: Iowa QB Nathan Stanley throws a strike down the sidelines to WR Ihmir Smith-Marsette, but the pass deflects off Smith-Marsette's helmet and Jacob Huff picks it off.
videos.headline: Minnesota defense forces 1st turnover

videos.description: Following the interception from Iowa QB Nathan Stanley, Minnesota QB Demry Croft forces a pass in the end zone and is picked off by Jake Gervase.
videos.headline: Iowa counters with own interception

videos.description: Iowa QB Nathan Stanley finds WR James Butler over the middle for a 19-yard gain, but is stripped by Minnesota DB Ken Handy-Holly for a turnover.
videos.headline: Handy-Holly forces fumble

videos.description: Iowa QB Nathan Stanley connects with TE Noah Fant down the sidelines for a 45-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Stanley connects with Fant for TD

videos.description: Minnesota RB Kobe McCrary goes airborne for a 1-yard touchdown in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: McCrary leaps into the end zone for TD

videos.description: Minnesota QB Demry Croft completes a pass on the outside to WR Tyler Johnson for a 63-yard gain.
videos.headline: Croft finds Johnson for huge gain
